《'''Hope World'''》是[[韓國|韓國]]男子組合[[防彈少年團|防彈少年團]]成員[[鄭號錫|j-hope]]的首張Mixtape，由[[Big_Hit娛樂|Big Hit娛樂]]和[[鄭號錫|j-hope]]製作，於2018年3月2日發行，主打歌為〈Daydream〉。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/103291|title=全世界都在聽 J-Hope 的故事！〈Hope World〉獲海外媒體大力報導|accessdate=2018-03-05|work=|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2018-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180305092612/https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/103291|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==背景==
《Hope World》是[[鄭號錫|j-hope]]繼成員[[金南俊|RM]]和[[閔玧其|SUGA]]後，第三位發表個人mixtape的[[防彈少年團|防彈少年團]]成員。[[鄭號錫|j-hope]]於訪問中說：「我想和這個世界分享我的故事。[[金南俊|RM]]和[[閔玧其|SUGA]]給了我很正面的影響，以自己的風格來創作音樂看起真的很帥，所以我也有了製作mixtape的動機。」<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/8238399/bts-j-hope-emerging-artists-chart-hope-world-ep/|title=J-Hope of BTS Debuts at No. 3 on Emerging Artists Chart|accessdate=2018-03-08|work=|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211116125159/https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/8238399/bts-j-hope-emerging-artists-chart-hope-world-ep/}}</ref>

==商業成績==
2018年3月2日，防彈少年團成員[[鄭號錫|j-hope]]推出首張Mixtape《Hope World》，並成為75個國家的[[iTunes|iTunes]]排行榜一位，是[[韓國|韓國]]solo歌手專輯的最高紀錄。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9F%93%E8%BF%B7/164727/bts%E9%98%B2%E5%BD%88%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E5%9C%98-j-hope%E6%8E%A8%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BAmixtape-hope-world-%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5%E5%88%B0%E8%82%9A%E7%97%9B|title=防【BTS防彈少年團】j-hope推個人MIXTAPE《HOPE WORLD》緊張到肚痛|accessdate=2018-03-03|work=hk01|language=zh-hans|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180430045605/https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9F%93%E8%BF%B7/164727/bts%E9%98%B2%E5%BD%88%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E5%9C%98-j-hope%E6%8E%A8%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BAmixtape-hope-world-%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5%E5%88%B0%E8%82%9A%E7%97%9B|archivedate=2018-04-30}}</ref>而《Hope World》中歌曲〈Daydream〉和〈Airplane〉的音樂錄影帶分別於3月2日和3月7日發佈。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://star.ettoday.net/news/1122306|title=防彈j-hope新歌「橫掃63國冠軍」　MV才出14hr點閱超狂|accessdate=2018-03-02|work=|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2018-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180722125857/https://star.ettoday.net/news/1122306|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年3月14日，《Hope World》 進入[[告示牌二百強專輯榜|Billboard 200]]第38名，刷新了自己上周持有的第63名記錄，並以第19名進入Top Rap Album。同時在Emerging Artists（新興藝人排行榜）排行第3、Artist 100排行第91名。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=011&aid=0003243197|title=방탄 제이홉‘Hope World’, 아이튠즈 63개국 1위…韓 솔로 최다기록|accessdate=2018-03-14|work=서울경제|language=ko|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612184702/http://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=011&aid=0003243197|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/8245045/j-hope-hope-world-second-week-sales-billboard-200-daydream-world-digital-song-sales-chart|title=J-Hope Rises on Billboard 200, Tops World Digital Song Sales in Second Week of 'Hope World'|accessdate=2018-03-14|work=billboard|language=en|archive-date=2019-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190410210214/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/8245045/j-hope-hope-world-second-week-sales-billboard-200-daydream-world-digital-song-sales-chart|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年12月5日，[[告示牌_(雜誌)|美國告示牌]]公布年末榜單，Mixtape《Hope World》分別登上World Album第5位及World Album Artist第6位。<ref>{{Cite web|url =https://www.billboard.com/articles/events/year-in-music-2018/8488875/year-in-k-pop-charts-bts-exo-blackpink-nct-127|title =The Year in K-Pop on the Charts: BTS Breaks Genre Barriers While the Scene Expands Its Reach|date =2018-12-06|language =en|accessdate =2020-07-01|archive-date =2018-12-06|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20181206164354/https://www.billboard.com/articles/events/year-in-music-2018/8488875/year-in-k-pop-charts-bts-exo-blackpink-nct-127|dead-url =no}}</ref>

2019年2月6日，去年3月發表的Mixtape《Hope World》在世界最大的音源流媒體平台[[Spotify|Spotify]]中達成了1億串流媒體紀錄，同時j-hope也成為了第2位在[[Spotify|Spotify]]關注人數突破100萬的[[韓國|韓國]]歌手。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://danmee.jp/knews/k-pop/btsnews-216/|title=TBTS(防弾少年団) J-HOPEは1億ストリーミング男! MIXTAPE「Hope World」がSpotifyで快挙|accessdate=2019-02-06|language=ja|archive-date=2019-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190207072444/http://danmee.jp/knews/k-pop/btsnews-216/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年8月3日，Mixtape《Hope World》主打歌〈[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OK3GJ0WIQ8s Daydream] {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OK3GJ0WIQ8s |date=20200112111354 }}〉的音樂錄影帶歷時518天突破1億瀏覽次數，成為[[防彈少年團|防彈少年團]]中第3位個人歌曲破億的成員。<ref>{{Cite web|url =https://www.soompi.com/article/1343085wpp/btss-j-hope-hits-100-million-views-with-daydream-mv|title =BTS’s J-Hope Hits 100 Million Views With “Daydream” MV|accessdate =2019-08-03|language =en|archive-date =2019-08-03|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20190803035643/https://www.soompi.com/article/1343085wpp/btss-j-hope-hits-100-million-views-with-daydream-mv|dead-url =no}}</ref>

